data.description: Simply stunning! Do not overlook this attractive 5 bedroom, 3 bathroom corner lot home that boasts nearly 3,000 sq. ft. of living space. So many updates and upgrades in this home include newer wood flooring throughout most of the main level, a fully renovated kitchen with newer cabinets, granite counter tops, backsplash and flooring. Open floor concept, fireplace, formal dining room, formal living or office, and bedroom are on the main level. The second level offers 4 additional bedrooms including the primary suite that has a sitting room, double walk-in closets, and luxurious en-suite bathroom. This home has a fully fenced yard, roof was recently replaced, and it has a high efficiency HVAC. Great location within minutes to Bentonville.
